# LocalAngel UI/UX & Atomic Design Rules


globs: ["lib/**/*.dart"]
priority: 85


## Atomic Design & Theming


- Organize UI under `lib/design_system/`:
- `tokens/` (spacing, radii, durations, breakpoints, typography)
- `atoms/`, `molecules/`, `organisms/`, `templates/`
- Enforce Material 3: color scheme from a seed; responsive breakpoints; motion patterns via `animations`.
- Typography via `google_fonts`; no raw `TextStyle` inline—use tokens.


## Components


- Build reusable atoms (LAButton, LAIconButton, LAChip, LATextField), compose into molecules (UserCard, RewardTile), then organisms (GuardianList, AlertTimeline), then templates (DashboardTemplate).
- All components accept `Key`, expose minimal props, and are side‑effect free.


## Accessibility


- Provide `semanticsLabel`/`Tooltip` for icon-only controls; ensure 48x48dp min hit targets; support text scaling; test with TalkBack/VoiceOver.


## Motion & Polish


- Prefer subtle motion (`FadeThroughTransition`, `SharedAxisTransition`) and micro‑interactions on primary actions.


## Visual Quality


- Zero magic numbers; use design tokens. Avoid inline colors except in tokens/theme.